name: PainInExtremities
title: Pain in Extremities
description: "This value set may undergo changes until the HL7 Multiple Chronic Care FHIR IG is formally published in 2024."
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values reflect patients experiencing discomfort sensation in the upper or lower extremities.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this value set is to identify patients experiencing Pain in Extremities.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes Pain in Extremities related SNOMED CT codes from Findings hierarchy.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes Pain in Extremities related SNOMED CT codes from Disorder of body system (disorder) hierarchy.)
